data.description: Discover what island living is all about in this centrally located, beautiful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo. Nestled within the private Arbors gated community, this residence offers a seamless blend of luxury and convenience. Your new home awaits in a community boasting many amenities, including a spacious swimming pool and abundant guest parking, ensuring every day feels like a vacation.  Immerse yourself in the tranquility of this well-designed condo, featuring modern touches throughout. With its proximity to golf courses, local community parks, and easy access to the main freeway and malls, you're ideally situated to enjoy the best the island offers. Indulge in endless shopping and dining opportunities, making this property a home and a gateway to a vibrant and connected island lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to call this condo retreat yours. The seller is offering a $5000 Carpet allowance at closing.
